profile:
Enjoy Your Home & Let Us Handle The Mess!

Fast, efficient, and honest. Tidydens prides itself on our easy to use booking system and experienced cleaners. 

Great service begins and ends with experienced and friendly professionals, which is why we put so much consideration into selecting only the best to join our team. 

We want our customers to be satisfied with our work, which is why we provide open communication channels throughout the duration of each appointment and go above and beyond to form lasting relationships with our clients.
services:
#1 KITCHEN: 
- Clean sink, backsplash, exterior appliances, inside &  outside of the microwave, exterior cabinets, cabinet handles, light switches wiped, stovetop, stove hood, kitchen table/kitchen island, wipe exterior garbage can, move any papers or objects and organize them neatly
- Wipe down all countertops and horizontal surfaces

#2 BATHROOMS:
- Clean the sink(s), backsplash,  bathroom mirror(s), exterior cabinets and vanities, toilet bowl, the entire exterior surface of the toilet,  bathtub, shower, sink faucet, shower head, wipe down garbage can, detailed dusting on all surfaces
- Make sure bathrooms are very clean and no water spots or wiping streaks are anywhere

#3 WALLS + BASEBOARDS
- Spot-check all walls and any wiped down dirty walls. Important to make sure that all baseboards have been wiped. Walls and Baseboards in ALL areas in the home need to be spot-checked/wiped

#4 INTERIOR WINDOWS + WINDOWSILLS:
- Important to make sure that all interior windows have been wiped down. In addition, all window sills need to be wiped down and dusted

#5 INTERIOR + EXTERIOR FRIDGE + OVEN:
- Important to make sure that both the fridge and the oven are pulled out and inside, exterior, on top, and behind the fridge/oven are cleaned and wiped down. (Fridge must have all drawers and freezer drawers emptied and wiped.) In addition, the oven must have all racks removed and the entire interior sprayed and wiped down

#6 BEDROOMS:
- Make beds, pick up any clothing that is on the floor, make sure it looks tidy. Clean window sills, interior windows, detailed dusting on all horizontal surfaces, bedside tables, move any items on bedside tables and clean surfaces

#7 FLOORING: 
- Vacuum all carpet flooring throughout the home, bedrooms, hallways, living areas etc.
- Vacuum all hardwood surfaces/dry mop all surfaces, make sure all dust and anything is off the floor before wet mopping
- Wet mop all flooring, hardwood, tile, vinyl, etc

#8 GENERAL:
- Empty all garbage and recycling out of home
- Restock garbage bags in cans and bins
- Complete any additional customer requests 
- Complete a thorough walk-through of the whole property. Make sure nothing was missed and all tasks are completed on the list above

profile: There are plenty of reasons to choose -- and love -- MaidPro. Maybe it’s because we work with you to build a cleaning plan, tailored to your needs and budget. Or because our cleaning PROs are not only expertly trained to provide the highest quality clean, but they’re pretty great people too. It could be because we allow you to choose when and how often we clean so that we fit perfectly into your life and schedule. No matter the reason, at the end of the day cleaning is our passion and it’s what we bring to each and every home we touch. Here at MaidPro South Edmonton-Leduc, we strive to deliver the best total customer care package in South Edmonton, Leduc, Beaumont, and the surrounding area, offering all of our clients VIP treatment regardless of their budget and frequency of service. We are especially proud to stand behind MaidPro's 49-Point Checklist and are committed to improving the lives of every client with every clean. MaidPro cleaning PROs are professionally trained, bonded, insured, background-checked, and backed by a 24-hour Re-Clean Guarantee. If you're ever dissatisfied with your clean, we'll make it right!
products: At MaidPro, we customize our service to meet your needs and budget. We offer a full range of house cleaning services and use a 49-Point Checklist™ to ensure your home is cleaned correctly, every time, guaranteed. Kitchens, bathrooms, floors and dusting are our specialties. Beyond that, we focus on areas of your home selected by you.
services: It's time to discover the magic of MaidPro! Professional house cleaning is a very personal service, and we work closely with you to help customize your cleaning service around your unique needs and priorities. We offer weekly, bi-weekly and monthly house cleaning schedules, with no contracts. We also do one-time cleanings, from regular cleaning to heavy duty cleaning. Don't need everything cleaned? Don't worry we can design your maid service around your needs and budget.
brands: We believe that everyone should have a clean and healthy home. That’s why we make sure the products, tools and processes we use are in the best interest of our planet and every customer whose life we touch. All our products are the best in quality and safe for pets and people.
specialities: We know and trust our MaidPro employees on a personal and professional level. Our cleaning PROs undergo thorough background checks prior to employment and are bonded and insured. They also receive extensive maid service training to instill the skills needed to clean to the highest standards—yours! And while we strive to help our employees work to their greatest ability, we also make sure to have fun. Because when you love what you do, it shows in your work.
